{"tid":1992084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(28/4) 國防部發放海軍飛機錄影, 確認有UFO存在","createTime":"2020-04-28T02:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T06:23:14.000Z","uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f463ba1ddf2247d5d299aa334d29185a8f5e5714","tid":1992084,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:29:56.000Z","msg":"VIDEO 1/3 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/lWLZgnmRDs4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlWLZgnmRDs4&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=b60f2b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lWLZgnmRDs4</a> <br />\nVIDEO 2/3 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/2TumprpOwHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2TumprpOwHY&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=ffc6daa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2TumprpOwHY</a><br />\nVIDEO 3/3 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/VUrTsrhVce4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVUrTsrhVce4&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=e87b0be5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VUrTsrhVce4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLast modified on Tue 28 Apr 2020 03.10 BST<br />\n<br />\nThe Pentagon on Monday released three declassified videos that show US Navy pilots encountering what appear to be unidentified flying objects.<br />\n<br />\nThe grainy videos, which the Pentagon says depict &ldquo;unexplained aerial phenomena&rdquo;, were previously leaked, with some believing they show alien unidentified flying objects (UFOs).<br />\n<br />\nThe Pentagon said it released the footage to &ldquo;to clear up any misconceptions by the public on whether or not the footage that has been circulating was real or whether or not there is more to the videos,&rdquo; a statement on the Department of Defense website said.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;After a thorough review, the department has determined that the authorized release of these unclassified videos does not reveal any sensitive capabilities or systems, and does not impinge on any subsequent investigations of military air space incursions by unidentified aerial phenomena,&rdquo; the statement said.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/27/pentagon-releases-three-ufo-videos-taken-by-us-navy-pilots\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Fapr%2F27%2Fpentagon-releases-three-ufo-videos-taken-by-us-navy-pilots&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPtB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=fc9a032d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/apr/27/pentagon-releases-three-ufo-videos-taken-by-us-navy-pilots</a>"},{"pid":"ac066e762255103412e46db7bd9c9f2eddc86237","tid":1992084,"uid":103981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:32:50.000Z","msg":"所以有武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外星人策劃「占中」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" 